        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer257610075" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5180164518238750404">Amazing. There are a just a few books (Meditations, Decline and Fall of the Roman Empire, Brothers Karamazov) that I feel every person on the planet should read. This is one of those books. If you are a historian, a diplomat, a Civil War buff or an amateur philosopher, this book will strongly resonate.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


